{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"updateGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"forSourceId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"sourceId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"features","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature","text":"Feature"},{"text":"], ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"sourceId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A style source identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"features","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The GeoJSON features to be updated in the source."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}]}],"name":"dataId"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The update operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"code":"onSourceDataLoaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter to filter the events)","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onMapLoadingError"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"code":"type = metadata","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if data parsing error has occurred.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in a ","type":"text"},{"code":"map-loading-error","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the ","type":"text"},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"each batch will be included in the "},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError","type":"reference"},{"text":" if there is a problem updating features in the source.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Throws","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/updategeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager\/updateGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Style","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Update existing features in a GeoJSON style source.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"updateGeoJSONSourceFeatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"features","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","text":"Feature"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"updateGeoJSONSourceFe